  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, blockchain's immutability ensures the integrity and tamper-resistance of the audit trail.",
    "Once recorded on the blockchain, the information becomes practically unalterable, preventing unauthorised modifications or tampering.This feature ensures that the audit trail remains reliable and trustworthy, bolstering confidence in the accountability and transparency of AI systems.",
    "The use of blockchain technology also facilitates cross-organizational audits and accountability.",
    "Multiple stakeholders, including developers, data providers, regulators, and end-users, can access the blockchain-based audit trail and contribute to the auditing process.",
    "This collaborative approach enhances the effectiveness of audits, promotes shared responsibility, and strengthens the overall accountability framework surrounding AI systems."
  ],
